column2:
<color=@linkTextHoverColorLight>Radar</color>
Radar Modes:
    <color=@badTextColor>RWS</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Range-While-Scan</color> Mode | Sorts targets on the scope by range.
    <color=@badTextColor>ACQ</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Target Acquisition</color> Mode
    <color=@badTextColor>STT</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Single-Target Track</color> Mode

<color=@linkTextHoverColorLight>Radar/IRST</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Radar w/ Infrared Search-and-Track Sensor</color>
Radar Modes:
    <color=@badTextColor>RWS</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Range-While-Scan</color> Mode | Sorts targets on the scope by range.
    <color=@badTextColor>ACQ</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Target Acquisition</color> Mode
    <color=@badTextColor>STT</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Single-Target Track</color> Mode
IRST Modes:
    <color=@badTextColor>SRC IR</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>IR Search</color> Mode
    <color=@badTextColor>ACQ IR</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>IR Target Acquisition</color> Mode
    <color=@badTextColor>STT IR</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>IR Single-Target Track</color> Mode

<color=@linkTextHoverColorLight>IRST</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Infrared Search & Track</color>
IRST Modes:
    <color=@badTextColor>SRC IR</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>IR Search</color> Mode
    <color=@badTextColor>ACQ IR</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>IR Target Acquisition</color> Mode
    <color=@badTextColor>STT IR</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>IR Single-Target Track</color> Mode

<color=@linkTextHoverColorLight>Search Radar</color>
Radar Modes:
    <color=@badTextColor>RWS</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Range-While Scan</color> | Sorts targets on the scope by range.

<color=@linkTextHoverColorLight>Tracking Radar</color>
Radar Modes:
    <color=@badTextColor>ACQ</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Target Acquisition</color> Mode
    <color=@badTextColor>STT</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Single-Target Track</color> Mode

<color=@linkTextHoverColorLight>Radar Rangefinder</color>
Radar Modes:
    <color=@badTextColor>ACQ</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Rangefinder Target Acquisition</color> Mode
    <color=@badTextColor>STT</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Single-Target Track</color> Mode

<color=@badTextColor>LD-VS</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Look-Down Velocity Search</color> Mode | Aspect: <color=@chatActiveInfoColor>Head-On</color> | Sorts targets on the scope by relative closure rate instead of range.
<color=@badTextColor>TWS</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Look-Down Track-While-Scan</color> Mode | Tracks a single contact while scanning for others. Cannot be used to fire SARH missiles.
<color=@badTextColor>TWS+</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Look-Down Track-While-Scan+</color> Mode | Tracks a single contact while scanning for others. Cannot be used to fire SARH missiles.

<color=@badTextColor>ESA TWS</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Electronically-Scanned Array Look-Down Track-While-Scan</color> Mode | Tracks a single contact while scanning for others. Cannot be used to fire SARH missiles.

<color=@badTextColor>IFF</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Identification, Friend-or-Foe</color> | Differentiates friendly and enemy radar contacts. Friendly contacts are displayed with a line above them on the scope.
<color=@badTextColor>BVR</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Beyond Visual-Range</color> Combat Mode | Allows the radar to switch to STT mode from RWS/TWS.
<color=@badTextColor>ACM</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Air Combat Mode</color> | Short-range radar boresight mode for dogfighting. Locks onto the closest/strongest radar contact.
<color=@badTextColor>HMS</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Helmet-Mounted Sight</color> | Allows IR missiles and/or the aircraft's radar to be slewed to wherever the cursor is pointing.

<color=@badTextColor>NCTR</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Non-Cooperative Target Recognition</color> | Displays identifying information about the aircraft being tracked by the radar.
    - Recognized Threat Types
<color=@badTextColor>CW</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Continuous-Wave Guidance</color> Mode | Allows the radar to guide SARH missiles in STT mode.

<color=@badTextColor>DL</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Radar/Missile Datalink</color> | Allows the radar to provide positioning updates to missiles with a DL mode.
    - Total DL Channels

Launch Warning: <color=@goodTextColor>Yes</color>
  Maximum Tracked Launches on Scope
Range by Signal Strength: <color=@goodTextColor>Yes</color> | Approximates the range of a contact on the RWR scope based on the strength of its radar signal.
Sensor Suite: <color=@linkTextHoverColorLight>Radar/IRST</color> - <color=@userlogColoredText>Radar + Infrared Search-and-Track Sensor</color> | Model
